### ==============================================================
### Clinical Triage - API Test Suite (REST Client)
### ==============================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1/patients


### 1. Register a new patient (Urgency: EMERGENCY)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Marcus Johnson",
    "symptoms": "Severe chest pain and shortness of breath",
    "urgency": "EMERGENCY"
}

### --------------------------------------------------------------

### 2. Register a new patient (Urgency: URGENT)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Sarah Williams",
    "symptoms": "High fever (39.5C) and dizziness",
    "urgency": "URGENT"
}

### --------------------------------------------------------------

### 3. Register a new patient (Urgency: NORMAL)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "David Chen",
    "symptoms": "Sprained ankle, pain when walking",
    "urgency": "NORMAL"
}

### --------------------------------------------------------------

### 4. Get all patients in the triage queue
### (Expected: Sorted by Status then by Registration Time)
GET {{baseUrl}}

### --------------------------------------------------------------

### 5. Update patient status to 'IN_TREATMENT'
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/1/status?status=IN_TREATMENT

### --------------------------------------------------------------

### 6. Update patient status to 'DISCHARGED'
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/1/status?status=DISCHARGED

### --------------------------------------------------------------

### 7. Update patient status to 'WAITING'
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/1/status?status=WAITING